 + - This File, Version		 : 0.7.1
 + - This File, Programming Code : Pure Pre-Hyper-Text-Post-Processor
 + - Programming Code Model	 : Procedural, Functional, Object Oriented :: Pre-Order Algebraic
 + -				 :					   :: Pre-Order Logical
